    <p>(b) Company reserves the right to exercise sole control over the defense, at Buyer&rsquo;s expense, of any claim subject to indemnification under this Section 14.5.&nbsp; This indemnity is in addition to, and not in lieu of, any other indemnities set forth in a written agreement between Buyer and Company.</p>

